usercommand:
Listed commands will be showned in the newz-bot-channel with in the discord server to save flooding the general channel for other users please look there for commands you use.



Timer Commands:

sat spawn                    - Shows the aliens spawn time in the newz-bot-channel.


Loot Commands:

sat loot rifles               - will show the rifles loot table.
sat loot snipers           - will show the snipers loot table.
sat loot pistols            - will show the pistols loot table.
sat loot melee             - will show the melee loot table.
sat loot ammo             - will show the ammos loot table.
sat loot backpacks      - will show the backpacks loot table.
sat loot consumables - will show the consumables loot table.
sat loot armor              - will show the armors loot table.
sat loot various            - will show the various items loot table.


Skin commands:

sat skins chrome          - this will show all the chrome skins prices
sat skins hynx               - this will show all the hynx skins prices
sat skins dreadnaught - this will show all the dread naught skins prices
sat skins infinity           - this will show all the infinity skins prices
sat skins neondragon  - this will show all the neon dragon skins prices
sat skins reddragon     - this will show all the redragon skins prices
